name: Entrenched (James1236)
description:
Swipe or use the arrow keys to move around, dig deeper and deeper to upgrade your mining machine! Avoid impassable rocks and when you run out of battery, go to the upgrades page to improve your mining capabilities. The generated worlds are deep and full of different resources to mine.

Credits: Bobaloney, Loopiloop, Origedit, sawdust, Tzomby, Sounak9434, ViChyavIn, Martin Magni
